2013年6月12日







Some of the outdated tech skills and withering technologies





Many IT professionals, from engineers to help desk support workers to system administrators, have significant XP experience. Unfortunately, this may no longer be a useful attribute.

(不要寫XP)



須知


how to manage software services and software configurations in the cloud. 




The explosion of smartphones, apps and real-time location information - and especially social media recommendation - is diminishing the importance of search results. 


Something That Seems Secure Today  


The TIOBE Programming Community Index lists 



C, Java, C++ and Objective-C as the programming skills most in demand right now.


The only solution is to keep learning - and keep showing that you can learn 


 free and low-cost resources like Khan Academy and CodeAcademy, for example.  









