[2]Wen-Chung Kao, Jia-An Ye, Ming-I Chu, and Chung-Yen Su, “Image quality improvement for electrophoretic displays by combining contrast enhancement and halftoning techniques,” IEEE Trans. Consumer Electronics, vol. 55, no. 1, pp. 15 - 19, Feb. 2009.
[3]Wen-Chung Kao, Jia-An Ye, Fong-Shou Lin, Craig Lin, and Robert Sprague, “Configurable timing controller design for active matrix electrophoretic display with 16 gray levels,” in Proc. IEEE International Conference Consumer Electronics (ICCE), Las Vegas, January 2009. (EI)
